{"tid":2331159,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚唔溝女","createTime":"2020-12-18T14:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T16:29:42.000Z","uid":135811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd00deb6d033904c8e45185caf5d6e40406669e","tid":2331159,"uid":135811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T14:23:26.000Z","msg":"係因為毒撚冇女埋身 定毒撚唔識溝女？<br />\n<br />\n哲學問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c044e7949872383175033d2ac1629029fc4ece","tid":2331159,"uid":135811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T14:24:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3b8e6bcc39ecafac4d5d32b859c7a7d8f07c0776","tid":2331159,"uid":135811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T14:25:07.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"57faec35081412695c879a7afdb0319fe1b5a61d","tid":2331159,"uid":135811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T14:25:18.000Z","msg":"再三推"},{"pid":"be391eac3acb75ec18803992a10e90e0ae954945","tid":2331159,"uid":135811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T14:25:37.000Z","msg":"有冇毒撚解答吓"},{"pid":"b17b771630a930957cc2cdc8a577e210634a027f","tid":2331159,"uid":373794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:37:04.000Z","msg":"睇你邊隻毒撚？<br />\n因為毒撚真係分好多隻。。。<br />\n我知佢地都有共同特徵，但各有特點&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n以下純個人意見<br />\n<br />\n1.(不同喜好的發燒友)毒撚<br />\n<br />\n    呢種毒撚有自己嘅喜好<br />\n   例如巴膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nfigure/模型膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n       軍事膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oJxysKT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoJxysKT.jpg&h=3fd9bd8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地嘅喜好非常獨特，所以同其他人無太多共通話題，自然無咩女溝。<br />\n但係佢地都有<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"green\">正常人嘅社交能力</span></span>，所以最後都會成功脫毒。<br />\n<br />\n2.(刻板印象)毒撚<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">大眾</span></span>認為呢種人喜愛ACG，屋企會有各種自己喜愛的角色的收藏品。性格懦弱，怕事，不合群，被人欺凌，事實上佢地同正常人無異，只不過大眾對於acg界的偏見實在太嚴重。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LkBCUpr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLkBCUpr.jpg&h=05d1f94c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/handup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以佢地有女，都唔怪，你地唔好話佢係「偽」毒<br />\n<br />\n3.(專業人士)毒撚<br />\n<br />\n佢地真係專業人士，工程師、會計師...乜乜師，甚至佢地係acg界/其他範疇嘅專業鑑賞員，無論你覺得佢幾撚「毒」，甚至隔著個mon都聞都佢陣「毒」味，佢哋都係值得尊重，佢已經獲得一定嘅成就，對於自己喜愛嘅事情，佢地有下苦功。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YDP804a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYDP804a.png&h=75f730b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論佢地有無另一半，佢地都唔應該被你貶低價值。<br />\n<br />\n4.真&bull;毒撚<br />\n你成日喺電視見到個啲「我覺得自己係零」「這些機會不是屬於我的」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xRvDDQu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxRvDDQu.jpg&h=5e70b8f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我成世人剩係見過兩個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係真係「真&bull;毒撚」<br />\n<br />\n所以真毒撚係萬中無一，非常罕見。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋無經濟壓力，有父母親養佢<br />\n無返學，無返工，無受訓<br />\n你問佢：點解你唔點點點xyz ？<br />\n佢答：唔知啊~無動力囉~<br />\n<br />\n平日除咗食飯屙屎等等之外，最鍾意打飛機(自慰)，佢地嘅樣係十分之猥瑣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係一個樣貌3/10嘅撚樣，我有小小暗瘡同爆牙突下巴，但佢地個樣十分正常6/10，但由於佢地缺乏<span class=\"red\">社交能力</span>，注意！！是<span class=\"red\">社交能力</span>，不是<span class=\"green\">溝通技巧</span>，佢地發音正常，可以正常傳達信息，但缺乏社交技巧，所以我(外貌不討好)反而可以有正常嘅社交圈子。<br />\n<br />\n例子#1 <br />\n             朋友A：&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n                佢：你知唔知我呢&hellip;我呢&hellip;我尋日昨咗人地個場，偷偷地搞死咗佢地(描述自己的遊戲場景)<br />\n             朋友A：噢！係啊~😅<br />\n                 佢：係囉&hellip;佢地好衰&hellip;成日搞人個場，所以尋日咪報&hellip;報復返佢&hellip;<br />\n             朋友A：&hellip;<br />\n                佢：&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n                佢：除咗尋日個件事之外，我&hellip;我呢我&hellip;想去donki好耐，一直無機會去&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n     忽現，有一隻惡犬路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n                佢：waaa....woo...dllm...waaa<br />\n             朋友A：😅唔使驚喎<br />\n                佢：啊&hellip;係啊，我驚狗呀，所以係囉&hellip;&hellip;sorry ah sor sor sor<br />\n              <br />\n例子#2<br />\n                伯母：仔呀，記得幫我熄電器，我落街買野呀&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n                  佢：係呀，係呀，得啦，你落去啦。<br />\n         伯母出咗門<br />\n                 佢：屌，咁撚煩嘅(自言自語)<br />\n<br />\n呢種毒撚如果要脫毒，最好要戒丁，令自己心態平伏，先可以消除戾氣同狗公相。<br />\n<br />\n唔識社交，並不是叫你收埋自己，一世都唔同人講野，最緊要同人講多啲野，實戰愈多，先會愈有自信。<br />\n一開頭，可以同自己較親近的父母吹水，學識尊重人，然後慢慢可以搵社工，安排副導小組/參加興趣班學習社交。<br />\n<br />\n最後都可以脫毒。"},{"pid":"6a2859e547f28b4d7c1b9f69dd469bebd8c7e8c8","tid":2331159,"uid":135811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"8c438771d7862cfe15d10857e272c046e6f600af","tid":2331159,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:03:28.000Z","msg":"試過溝女<br />\n俾啲女一巴打過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0a9b9cfd1b238d8c7b5b2697e935ef5ced32be","tid":2331159,"uid":135811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c438771d7862cfe15d10857e272c046e6f600af","tid":2331159,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:03:28.000Z","msg":"試過溝女<br />\n俾啲女一巴打過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}